# OHOS standalone executable support for `bun build --compile`
#
# Two logical changes in one cfg-gated patch:
#   1. mod elf::imp (OHOS): parse /proc/self/exe SHT to locate `.bun`
#      section (replaces Bun__getStandaloneModuleGraphELFVaddr FFI).
#   2. inject_into_binary (OHOS): ftruncate(0) before write_all +
#      fsync before post-truncate, to defeat COW/reflink + stale
#      copy_file_range reads.
#
# Upstream reference: springmin/bun ohos-aarch64 @ 39d8416e
# OpenSpec change: ohos-bun-standalone-compile

